      "disable": "<p>@Check[type:acrobatics|dc:16] to dodge, @Check[type:athletics|dc:17] to outrun the disaster, @Check[type:survival|dc:19] (trained) to seek shelter in rocky terrain; if accessible, @Check[type:Life Science Lore|dc:15] (trained) or @Check[type:nature|dc:17] or @Check[type:religion|dc:17] (trained) to generate a protective barrier using life essence from nearby outcroppings. On a successful check to generate a protective barrier, grant a +2 status bonus to each PC's checks to disable the hazard for the remainder of the event. Four total successes are required to disable the hazard.</p>",
